# This file describes objects in the world for AVM processing
# Hashes start commented lines.
#
# The format of each (non-comment) line is as follows:
# {type:TYPE attribute1:value1 ... attributeN:valueM}
#
# Where:
#    TYPE is the attribute type (for which a corresponding structure must
#         be specified in the domain's AVMStructure file
#
# Minimal example:
#{type:tile name:x label:x1 color:green ord:1 orient:top row_col:row ord:1 orient:bottom row_col:row ord:1 orient:left row_col:col ord:1 orient:right row_col:col tb:top lr:left desc:corner relation:next_to relation:above relation:below}
